                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 142.) I went to Mrs. Nicholls with the witness, M'Bane, and she delivered these things up to me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">M'Bane's Defence.</hi> I went to call Glenning, as we were going up into the fields together; I asked my brother if he would come; he said, "No;" we went, and about half an hour after my brother came.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Glenning's Defence.</hi> I went up into the fields with M'Bane, and about half an hour after he came up.</p>
